1. *Podigni* glas (Raise your voice).
2. On je *podigao* ruke (He raised his hands).
3. Ona je *podigla* razred (She lifted the class).
4. Oni su *podigli* svoje čaše (They raised their glasses).
5. Mi smo *podigli* svoje glasove (We raised our voices).
6. Oni su *podigli* sebe (They raised themselves).